1. OS를 왜 배우는가?
- Understand how computers really work
- Understand concurrency
- Build large reliable systems
- Understand performance tradeoffs
즉
Systems Thinking을 배우기 위함

2. OS란?
OS = resource manager + abstraction provider
hardware resources를 관리하고
applications에 abstraction을 제공하는 시스템

1-1. Resource Manager 자원 관리자
CPU : scheduling
memory : allocation
disk : file system
network
devices : driver
등 제한된 자원을 공정하고 효율적으로 분배하기 위함

1-2. Abstraction Provider 추상화 제공
disk → block read/write
CPU → registers
memory → physical address

ex)
hardware : abstraction
CPU : process
memory : virtual memory
disk : file
network : socket


